  + [reason] is Fejer improved 3 of 9 sampled rows and worsened 6 of 9 sampled rows against exact psi(x)
  + [next_relevant_periphery] is Euler-product or logarithmic-derivative weighting, plus larger controlled windows if a new source-defined smoothing question requires them
